#

Spicy Honey Garlic Shrimp with Coconut Rice

25 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

AsianAmerican

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickFlavorfulSeafood

Description

A quick and flavorful dish featuring succulent shrimp coated in a spicy honey garlic sauce, served over creamy coconut rice.

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • honey: 1/4 cup
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 3 cloves
  • red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • coconut milk: 1 cup
  • white rice: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • green onions (sliced for garnish): 1/4 cup
